#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.reindex_like.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.reindex\\_like"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex_like:1 of
msgid "Return an object with matching indices as other object."
msgstr "返回一个与另一个对象具有匹配索引的对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex_like:3 of
msgid ""
"Conform the object to the same index on all axes. Optional filling logic,"
" placing NaN in locations having no value in the previous index. A new "
"object is produced unless the new index is equivalent to the current one "
"and copy=False."
msgstr ""
"使对象在所有轴上符合相同的索引。可选的填充逻辑，将 NaN 放置在先前索引中"
"没有值的位置。除非新索引与当前索引等效且 copy=False，否则将生成一个新对象"
"。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex_like of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex_like:8 of
msgid ""
"Its row and column indices are used to define the new indices of this "
"object."
msgstr "其行和列索引用于定义此对象的新索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex_like:11 of
msgid ""
"Method to use for filling holes in reindexed DataFrame. Please note: this"
" is only applicable to DataFrames/Series with a monotonically "
"increasing/decreasing index.  * None (default): don't fill gaps * pad / "
"ffill: propagate last valid observation forward to next   valid * "
"backfill / bfill: use next valid observation to fill gap * nearest: use "
"nearest valid observations to fill gap."
msgstr ""
"用于在重新索引的 DataFrame 中填充空洞的方法。请注意：这仅适用于具有单调"
"递增/递减索引的 DataFrames/Series。  * None（默认）：不填充空缺 * pad / "
"ffill：将上一个有效观测值向前传播到下一个有效值 * backfill / bfill：使用"
"下一个有效观测值填充空缺 * nearest：使用最近的有效观测值填充空缺。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex_like:11 of
msgid ""
"Method to use for filling holes in reindexed DataFrame. Please note: this"
" is only applicable to DataFrames/Series with a monotonically "
"increasing/decreasing index."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex_like:15 of
msgid "None (default): don't fill gaps"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex_like:16 of
msgid "pad / ffill: propagate last valid observation forward to next valid"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex_like:18 of
msgid "backfill / bfill: use next valid observation to fill gap"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex_like:19 of
msgid "nearest: use nearest valid observations to fill gap."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex_like:21 of
msgid "Return a new object, even if the passed indexes are the same."
msgstr "即使传递的索引相同，也返回一个新对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex_like:23 of
msgid "Maximum number of consecutive labels to fill for inexact matches."
msgstr "不精确匹配时要填充的最大连续标签数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex_like:25 of
msgid ""
"Maximum distance between original and new labels for inexact matches. The"
" values of the index at the matching locations must satisfy the equation "
"``abs(index[indexer] - target) <= tolerance``.  Tolerance may be a scalar"
" value, which applies the same tolerance to all values, or list-like, "
"which applies variable tolerance per element. List-like includes list, "
"tuple, array, Series, and must be the same size as the index and its "
"dtype must exactly match the index's type."
msgstr ""
"不精确匹配时原始标签与新标签之间的最大距离。索引在匹配位置的值必须满足"
"方程 ``abs(index[indexer] - target) <= tolerance``。容差可以是一个标量值"
"，对所有值应用相同的容差，或者类似列表的形式，对每个元素应用不同的容差。"
"类似列表的包括列表、元组、数组、Series，并且必须与索引大小相同，其"
"数据类型必须与索引的类型完全匹配。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex_like:25 of
msgid ""
"Maximum distance between original and new labels for inexact matches. The"
" values of the index at the matching locations must satisfy the equation "
"``abs(index[indexer] - target) <= tolerance``."
msgstr ""

